FOF 4.0.0.a1
================================================================================

Backwards compatibility notes
----------------------------------------
* FOF has been rewritten in version 4 and breaks b/c. Good news: you can have FOF 3 and FOF 4 run side by side thanks to
  the new version using a different namespace.

